{"tid":1032288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★內地漢向高院提司法覆核，要求入境處撤銷拒絕他延期留港的決定","createTime":"2019-02-22T09:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T14:23:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe0efb91bf907aa463709ddaa8adfb055ccd5e7","tid":1032288,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"一名持中國護照人士2010年向港府申請以「資本投資者入境計劃」來港居留，翌年年底持中國護照來港，獲發香港身份證並准在港居留2年。至2014年初，他申請改用非洲國家畿內亞比紹護照繼續留港申請，但之後他稱其移民代理無通知他要提交補充資料，累他延期留港的申請被拒絕，他更因此在去年因涉嫌逾期留港被檢控。他現向高院提出司法覆核申請，要求入境處撤銷拒絕他延期留港的決定。<br />\n<br />\n這宗司法覆核的申請人朱俊(譯音)在申請書表示，入境處沒有直接向他提出要求補充文件，亦沒提示他在申請被拒後繼續留港會被檢控，是程序錯誤和違反自然公正原則。因此其決定欠缺法理基礎，應予撤銷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190222/bkn-20190222134943387-0222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190222%2Fbkn-20190222134943387-0222_00822_001.html&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLcyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=cf74596b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190222/bkn-20190222134943387-0222_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3ceb94651b66a2e621b74bc46e0069fc6d965c45","tid":1032288,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"司法覆核即時批公屋<br />\n<br />\n司法覆核即時批老綜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25891c99567dba6dba86eb41deec3dc54eb0460","tid":1032288,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1L5v5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1L5v5t.png&h=c0635f82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eebaf67a8b0016a08aae5850d0deb5d529dca5f","tid":1032288,"uid":130695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":